{"tid":2330126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中立d 咁講 其實怪HSBC 都冇用","createTime":"2020-12-17T17:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T18:32:25.000Z","uid":146917,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"516d95b1c25f98c6907b5f75144f817dd7725bc4","tid":2330126,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒 香港用邊間銀行都一樣<br />\n只可以話點解針對hsbc 只係因為佢地係hsbc都有戶口 eg 星火 議員等等 <br />\n如果話只係因為&quot;聽話&quot;而bam 佢地 我覺得就未必<br />\n姐係轉個話 如果星火 議員開citibank 戶口都會比人bam<br />\n因為all of 香港銀戶都係under HKMA 姐係係跟&ldquo;香港法律&rdquo; 所以唔一定比面外國<br />\n咁大家會好奇點解議員講極都唔化 唔開citibank？<br />\n因為政客身份開戶會比較難同唔一定開比佢<br />\n但我相信議員一定有去citibank 開 只不過係開唔到 or 等處理文件有掛先有通知<br />\n因為之前星火都想係citibank 到開戶 但係citiabnk唔批 咁代唔代表citibank 奶共？<br />\n得罪講句 如果針對hsbc bam 戶口佢地錯唔晒 但其他方面可以再做好d<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好多人仲鐘意用hsbc<br />\n<br />\n本台記者翻查谷歌搜尋趨勢，發現跟移民有關的關鍵字，例如「<span class=\"red\">移民英國</span>」，「移民台灣」，「移民澳大利亞」及「移民加拿大」，都成為熱搜；另一組熱門關鍵字則和離岸戶口相關，包括「<span class=\"red\">離岸戶口HSBC</span>」，「離岸戶口渣打」，「離岸戶口Citibank」及「離岸戶口DBS」，以上銀行全是香港外資銀行。"},{"pid":"7d8c52df0026bb48e8298830a77da1f15b7c6184","tid":2330126,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"樓下係on9仔"},{"pid":"5742579983a9dbdc427558860044ffef9a47eb7f","tid":2330126,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9c3e251bb0629af18942a8ad0b752253e106f8","tid":2330126,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img 